{
  "description": "std-stat-rows — a vertical stack of stat-badge rows rendered from a config-driven list. Exemplar for dynamic collection rendering over an arbitrary container: `(array/map @entity.rows (fn item …))` sits directly in a `children:` position, so no `renderItem` pattern is needed; the map lambda binds each row's fields with `@item.<field>`.",
